<p>Yaaaaay more tales! This was a collaborative writing effort between myself and lurkd, and was a ton of fun to do. I STRONGLY SUPPORT ADDITIONAL PROJECTS LIKE THIS IN THE FUTURE.</p>
<p>Anyway, thanks to everyone in chat who had a gander at this and gave ideas/critique, and thanks to lurkd for generally being super cool.</p>
<p>This tale sets up two new characters in the series, Dietrich Lurk and Alexandra, the AI! Excitement abounds, yes.</p>
<p>Thanks again everyone, and hope you enjoy this one!</p>
