														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2264596">
									

<p>This has an inevitable problem that you'll always end up running into with story-based canons or series at some point when you set them up; it feels too integral to the larger plot to standalone, but sets things up neccesarily in order to make sense for later installments.</p>
<p>I can't also say I like Dietrich's character much (kind of grates on me), though the addition of him being affected by 1471 is a nice touch. So no vote overall.</p>

