														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2264760">
									

<p>Nice to see the AIC stuff getting linked in.</p>
<p>On the subject of Dietrich's character: I quite liked him. His mannerisms strongly remind me of some of the more experienced engineers I've met, and having 1471 along for the ride gives him a whole range of complications that provide interesting plot fodder. He has been fit into the setting nicely, for a character who has relatively little written about him we have got a decent number of established relationships with recurring or potentially recurring characters (the AIs, now Aktus and 1471).</p>

							</div>

								
					
