			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2264940">
									

<p>I didn't get to see the new version of this before it went live, but I'm very happy to see that basically all my concerns were addressed quite nicely. This is fun. I like it.</p>
<p>Edit: my favorite expansion is the explicit use of 1471.</p>
<p>It's one of the few Resurrection threads that I don't know the plan for, too, so I'm excited to see where it goes.</p>

